      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity for Ti-6Al-4V is well-established for quasi-static implant loading. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces is consistent with published tribological data for titanium alloy interfaces. The model form is appropriate for the QoIs of interest (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm). Gradation 3 achieved."
