      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 (static compression-bending at 10 mm offset). While this represents the standard regulatory test condition, only a single load level was evaluated. This limits the ability to confirm model fidelity across the broader COU loading envelope. Gradation 2 achieved against a required Gradation 3; this factor is below the required level and is a noted gap in the credibility argument."
