      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in the FEA replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry: superior block fixed, inferior block loaded at 10 mm anterior offset. Material properties and geometry are derived from the same production lot as the test constructs. Load application rate is quasi-static in both simulation and experiment. Equivalency is documented in the V&V plan. Gradation 3 achieved."
