      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) were compared using the E/uval metric with pre-specified acceptance bound of 1.96. E/uval values of 0.81, 0.94, and 1.12 were obtained respectively. Percent differences of 1.2%, 1.3%, and 2.1% are all below the 10% bound. Acceptance criteria are met for all three QoIs. Gradation 3 achieved."
